The paper discusses the Internet of Things (IoT) and its applications, which falls under the category of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). It also examines the technologies used and functionalities of IoT solutions, which could be classified as Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Software Engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the classification of IoT solutions based on their application domains, which could be classified as Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
